{
  "stem": "13213.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in touch with some people that had some knowledge of partisans which were stationed in the forests of Pinsk, which was east of Rafalowka.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the forest started-- was not far from this town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said that the Jews were welcome to join.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing is now to get out of the town of Rafalowka which the town was surrounded by German guards all over the place, all over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, there was a very important railway station in Rafalowka, which the supplies were going to the Eastern Front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And second, they knew there were a lot of people who run away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And between them would be Jews and all kinds of partisans, and they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the partisans were already at that time attacking the Germans all over, so there were guards all over the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We found out from these people, like I say, that the partisans are maybe about 20 kilometers away, and if you can just cross, like, a border, from-- getting out into the woods, you would be safe.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We made a few attempts to, like, to spy on the Germans and the guards, where they were staying, at the railway station, at the road which you can cross.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we saw the guards standing everywhere, and it was impossible to find a place where you could just pass.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This young lady was with us, and she was begging us, we shouldn't leave her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was all alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know she-- she survived and she was-- I think her name was Bela, but I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We tried about two or three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day, we decided we'll make the move.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
